00:37:50,920 --> 00:37:51,560
You don't even have to talk.

877
00:37:53,440 --> 00:37:54,120
Just sit there.

878
00:37:54,120 --> 00:37:54,960
Nice and quiet.

879
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:57,840
I want Bing to try being a woman once.

880
00:37:59,880 --> 00:38:00,520
Would you want to?

881
00:38:00,880 --> 00:38:01,760
Bing, do you want to?

882
00:38:04,680 --> 00:38:05,320
I could.

883
00:38:05,600 --> 00:38:07,080
Let Bing experience

884
00:38:07,080 --> 00:38:09,000
what it's like to fly in the sky.

885
00:38:09,600 --> 00:38:10,280
Bragging...

886
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:15,600
Reach out and there's the hoop.

887
00:38:15,600 --> 00:38:16,600
Shoot and you score.

888
00:38:17,280 --> 00:38:18,080
Still talking about basketball.

889
00:38:20,960 --> 00:38:21,320
Alright.

890
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:22,680
I've got it figured out.

891
00:38:23,080 --> 00:38:24,280
Guess we'll all be making dumplings.

892
00:38:33,040 --> 00:38:33,600
Anyu.

893
00:38:33,600 --> 00:38:34,320
Anyu.

894
00:38:41,160 --> 00:38:41,920
I just want

895
00:38:41,920 --> 00:38:43,120
to not think about anything for a year.

896
00:38:47,160 --> 00:38:48,800
Just want to visit your mind.

897
00:38:53,160 --> 00:38:53,720
Here I am.

898
00:38:55,160 --> 00:38:56,440
Forget about gender—

899
00:39:10,800 --> 00:39:11,600
you're older than him.

900
00:39:13,600 --> 00:39:15,240
Teng and I are probably out of the running.

901
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:17,000
If you're talking about that...

902
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:18,200
finding a father-in-law or something...

903
00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:20,960
the two of us could join in.

904
00:39:20,960 --> 00:39:21,200
Right?

905
00:39:21,200 --> 00:39:22,080
We don't really stand a chance.

906
00:39:22,080 --> 00:39:23,320
Bing and I are out, Jingyu.

907
00:39:23,320 --> 00:39:23,760
No way.

908
00:39:24,720 --> 00:39:25,160
Still no.

909
00:39:25,160 --> 00:39:25,400
You two...

910
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:25,920
You're not up for it.

911
00:39:28,040 --> 00:39:28,320
Say it.

912
00:39:31,560 --> 00:39:32,800
Just these two aren't as good as him.

913
00:39:34,520 --> 00:39:35,880
The rest could compete.

914
00:39:37,840 --> 00:39:39,680
Men this outstanding...

915
00:39:41,080 --> 00:39:41,520
Seriously.

916
00:39:42,640 --> 00:39:43,600
He's really well-rounded.

917
00:39:43,600 --> 00:39:44,240
True.

918
00:39:45,280 --> 00:39:46,360
This show was the right choice.

919
00:39:50,280 --> 00:39:51,440
I feel like the only thing

920
00:39:51,440 --> 00:39:52,320
I might be a bit better than Jingyu at

921
00:39:54,960 --> 00:39:56,080
is maybe gaming—I might play better.

922
00:39:56,920 --> 00:39:58,400
Why does that girl like you for that?

923
00:40:00,160 --> 00:40:01,240
She's a game booster.

924
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:07,440
I'm really competitive on this one.

925
00:40:10,440 --> 00:40:11,760
I'm braver than Jingyu.

926
00:40:13,400 --> 00:40:15,520
I jump before Jingyu does.

927
00:40:16,200 --> 00:40:16,680
Jump first.

928
00:40:16,680 --> 00:40:17,280
Bungee jumping.

929
00:40:19,560 --> 00:40:20,280
That's a stretch.

930
00:40:22,040 --> 00:40:23,120
Only two of us even jumped.

931
00:40:28,960 --> 00:40:29,480
Thinking it over...

932
00:40:29,480 --> 00:40:31,120
doesn't seem like I'm better at anything else.

933
00:40:31,120 --> 00:40:31,800
Right?

934
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:33,960
Physical strength, physical strength...

935
00:40:36,720 --> 00:40:38,160
Guess we'll have to compare brains.

936
00:40:39,680 --> 00:40:41,800
See if the girl likes granite.

937
00:40:43,520 --> 00:40:44,520
Granite? What's that about?

938
00:40:45,920 --> 00:40:47,080
Granite head.

939
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:48,200
Stubborn and hard-headed.

940
00:40:50,320 --> 00:40:51,520
Still didn't get it.

941
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:55,760
I'm out.

942
00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:58,160
This episode...

943
00:40:58,160 --> 00:40:59,840
You're not "Stick Bro" anymore.

944
00:41:00,240 --> 00:41:00,720
"Granite Bro."

945
00:41:00,720 --> 00:41:01,360
"Granite Bro."

946
00:41:04,840 --> 00:41:06,000
Guess I'll just write myself.

947
00:41:07,480 --> 00:41:08,240
Even though on the question...

948
00:41:08,240 --> 00:41:09,560
we admit we're not as good, right?

949
00:41:09,960 --> 00:41:11,680
But we still have to write our own names.

950
00:41:19,640 --> 00:41:20,720
I wrote "no one."

951
00:41:20,720 --> 00:41:22,480
Darn it, Fan Chengcheng crossed it out and wrote himself.

952
00:41:24,320 --> 00:41:25,240
Is it really "no one"?

953
00:41:26,280 --> 00:41:27,400
You are me.

954
00:41:28,840 --> 00:41:29,600
Believe in yourself.

955
00:41:30,880 --> 00:41:32,200
Yeah, he's so confident.

956
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:33,040
I think...

957
00:41:33,680 --> 00:41:33,920
That's fine.

958
00:41:34,960 --> 00:41:35,800
Alright, just the two of us.

959
00:41:41,240 --> 00:41:42,120
Like a treasure hunt.

960
00:41:43,600 --> 00:41:44,360
I pick Teng.

961
00:41:49,920 --> 00:41:50,720
When did you start liking

962
00:41:51,400 --> 00:41:52,480
guys in their forties?

963
00:41:53,360 --> 00:41:53,840
No.

964
00:41:53,840 --> 00:41:56,080
I think what I can offer, everyone else can too.

965
00:41:56,320 --> 00:41:57,400
But this kind of

966
00:41:58,040 --> 00:41:58,600
happiness...

967
00:41:59,480 --> 00:42:00,880
We can't give as much as Teng does.

968
00:42:02,320 --> 00:42:02,760
Makes sense.

969
00:42:03,120 --> 00:42:03,560
Makes sense.

970
00:42:04,760 --> 00:42:06,480
Even the prettiest face ages.

971
00:42:06,480 --> 00:42:07,360
But still...

972
00:42:07,360 --> 00:42:09,240
Once it's aged, it doesn't matter anymore.

973
00:42:09,240 --> 00:42:09,720
Right?

974
00:42:15,240 --> 00:42:16,160
There's still something to gain.

975
00:42:18,520 --> 00:42:19,800
I love your show.

976
00:42:21,280 --> 00:42:22,560
I love every regular member.

977
00:43:22,720 --> 00:43:24,240
By season four, everyone will be a chef.

978
00:43:24,240 --> 00:43:25,040
Come on, let's get started.

979
00:43:29,040 --> 00:43:29,600
Great news!

980
00:43:29,600 --> 00:43:31,680
Of our five stars, which one do you like?

981
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:34,160
I'll make my specialty dish.

982
00:43:34,160 --> 00:43:35,960
A homemade tofu dish for everyone.

983
00:43:36,120 --> 00:43:36,560
Extra long.

984
00:43:36,560 --> 00:43:37,440
Cutting tofu this long.

985
00:43:37,440 --> 00:43:38,480
Extra-long tofu.

986
00:43:39,440 --> 00:43:40,640
Homestyle chicken wings.

987
00:43:40,640 --> 00:43:41,680
Just wait and see.

988
00:43:42,120 --> 00:43:42,760
Try it.

989
00:43:44,880 --> 00:43:46,760
Where's the batter? These aren't glazed wings.

990
00:43:47,400 --> 00:43:48,200
What is this?

991
00:43:48,480 --> 00:43:49,520
Candied chicken wings.

992
00:43:51,200 --> 00:43:52,320
It's not like I can't make it.

993
00:43:54,640 --> 00:43:55,160
There's a beefy taste.

994
00:43:55,160 --> 00:43:56,520
Feels like beef running on my tongue.

995
00:43:57,520 --> 00:43:58,680
Where are the top and bottom noodles?

996
00:44:00,120 --> 00:44:02,000
Now the pressure's on Teng's shredded potatoes.

997
00:44:02,720 --> 00:44:03,560
Go ahead and eat, in a bit.

998
00:44:03,560 --> 00:44:04,360
It's full of fingernails inside.

999
00:44:06,160 --> 00:44:06,920
Braised eggplant.

1000
00:44:08,200 --> 00:44:09,000
Grilled beef.

1001
00:44:09,520 --> 00:44:10,360
Time to eat.

1002
00:44:17,360 --> 00:44:19,400
You guys film first tomorrow morning.

1003
00:44:19,400 --> 00:44:20,480
Darn it, I'm off to lift weights.
